snippet.title: Mario Editor - Trailer
snippet.description:
With Mario Editor, it's easy to play, create, and share your very own custom Mario levels! Utilize a massive selection of powerups, enemies, items, and other goodies in your creations.

Download Game:
https://hellofangaming.github.io/wiki/Mario%20Editor.html

Mario Editor Showcase:
http://marioeditor.us.to/
Upload your levels, and download levels other people have made.

Music:
'2D Beat' by Arceace (http://ocremix.org)
'Caravan Bowser' by Flexstyle, XPRTNovice (http://ocremix.org)
